---
title: Crispy Baked Chicken and Mash with sweet and tangy Asian-inspired sauce
description: Golden baked breaded and butterflied chicken sits atop a bed of creamy mash in this simple recipe. Courgettes roasted until perfectly tender are the perfect accompaniment for a well-rounded meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R04_W16_IE_IEXFC0096-3_Main_high-269691a6.jpg
